headline: Humana Invites Everyone to Get in the Game With Pickleball Pop-Up Events
summary: LOUISVILLE, Ky., September 29, 2025--Humana invites everyone to get in the game with pickleball pop-up events at malls in Illinois, Indiana and Florida.
